<chapter id="policy-engine-configuracao">

    <title>Configuração do Policy Engine</title>

    <section>
        <title>Instalação do componente</title>
                <para>
            Para utilizar o componente <emphasis>policy-engine</emphasis> num projeto Java, 
            basta adicionar a sua dependência no arquivo <filename> pom.xml </filename>, conforme o seu gerenciador de projetos:
        </para>
        <para> <itemizedlist>
        		<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="https://maven.apache.org/">Apache-Maven</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA[
        		<dependency>
				<groupId>org.demoiselle.signer</groupId>
				<artifactId>policy-engine</artifactId>
				<version>4.3.0</version>
			</dependency>]]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        			<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="https://buildr.apache.org/">Apache Buildr</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA['org.demoiselle.signer:policy-engine:jar:4.3.0']]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        		<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="http://ant.apache.org/ivy/">Apache Ivy</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA[<dependency org="org.demoiselle.signer" name="policy-engine" rev="4.3.0" />]]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        	<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="http://docs.groovy-lang.org/latest/html/documentation/grape.html">Groovy Grape</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA[@Grapes(@Grab(group='org.demoiselle.signer', module='policy-engine', version='4.3.0'))]]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        	<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="https://github.com/grails/grails-gradle-plugin">Gradle/Grails</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA[<dependency org="org.demoiselle.signer" name="policy-engine" rev="4.3.0" />]]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        	<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="http://www.scala-sbt.org/">Scala SBT</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA[libraryDependencies += "org.demoiselle.signer" % "policy-engine" % "4.3.0"]]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        	<listitem>
        		 <para><ulink url="https://leiningen.org/">Leiningen</ulink></para>
        		 <para>
        		 	<programlisting ><![CDATA[<[org.demoiselle.signer/policy-engine "4.3.0"]]]>
			</programlisting>
        		 </para>
        		</listitem>
        	</itemizedlist>
        </para>
        
		<para> Caso não esteja utilizando nenhum outro tipo de gerenciador (estava morando numa caverna nos últimos dez anos), pode baixar o .jar do repositório:
		<para><ulink url="https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/demoiselle/signer/policy-engine/">https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/demoiselle/signer/policy-engine/</ulink></para>
		 
		</para>
        
    </section>

</chapter>
